      <title>迪拜门户网站寻找 Tim Horton Gulf 特许经营权的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/dubai-s-gateway-seeks-buyer-for-tim-horton-gulf-franchise-stake</link>
